CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 9, 1946, pg. 28, reads: "KIDDIES CELEBRATE - Adorable little Ann B. Cromartie, daughter of Pvt. and Mrs. Howard Cromartie, celebrated her first birthday at the home of her aunt, Mrs. Eula Jessup, of Wylie Avenue, last week. Guests were Elmer Jessup Jr., Leathia Blacks, Mayland Bryant, Shirley Lockett and Furman Maggett Jr. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Ann B. Cromartie seated on coffee table with cake for her first birthday party, with Elmer Jessup Jr., Leathia Blacks, Mayland Bryant, Shirley Lockett, and Furman Maggett Jr. seated on sofa, in home of Eula Jessup, Wylie Avenue
